### https://docs.livekit.io/transport/#mediaMedia

LiveKit enables realtime exchange of audio and video streams between participants. You can publish and subscribe to tracks, process raw media, apply noise cancellation, and export or import streams.
[Media overviewLearn how to handle realtime media tracks, screen sharing, and stream export/import in your applications.](https://docs.livekit.io/transport/media/)

